quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"S wavu iwezzâen!"
  51,2,"I ibubben taâkkwemt!"
  51,3,"Wid ippazalen s shala!"
  51,4,"Tid ifeôqen lameô!"
  51,5,"Ar ayen i wen ippuâahden, d tidep."
  51,6,"Aqeîîi, ih, ad iûaô."
  51,7,"S igenni bu idurra!"
  51,8,"Kunwi temgarradem $ef wawal."
  51,9,"Iooa t win iooan."
  51,10,"Tameppant i ikeddaben!"
  51,11,"Nitni, di maylellif, stehzan,"
  51,12,"steqsayen: ""anda t wass uqeîîi""?"
  51,13,"Ass ideg, ara ppuhewlen di tmes:"
  51,14,"""Jeôôbet ahewwel nnwen agi i$ef têarem""!"
  51,15,"Ih, wid ipêezziben, di leonanat akked tliwa;"
  51,16,"Ïîfen ayen i sen Ifka Mass nnsen. Ih, nitni llan, iu$ lêal, d lâuûam."
  51,17,"Deg iv, cwiî ay gganen."
  51,18,"Di tafrara, nitni ste$fiôen;"
  51,19,"deg wayla nnsen: amur i umappar akked ume$bun."
  51,20,"U di tmurt, issekniyen i wid ipputebbten."
  51,21,"Llant deg iman nnwen. Aâni ur tepwalim ara?"
  51,22,"U deg igenni, ôôeéq nnwen, akked wayen i wen ippuwaââden."
  51,23,"S Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, ar neppa d tidep, am akken kunwi tepmeslayem!"
  51,24,"Ma tebbwev ik id tedyant inebgawen ukyisen n Ibôahim?"
  51,25,"Kecmen $uôes, nnan as: ""tifrat""! Inna: ""tifrat a wid ur nessin!"""
  51,26,"Inser ar twacult is, ibbwi d aâjmi iqebbwan."
  51,27,"Iqeôb asen t id; inna: ""day ur teppeppem ara""?"
  51,28,"Iêus iugad iten. Nnan as: ""ur ppagwad""! D$a beccôen t s uqcic amusnaw"
  51,29,"Tqeôb ed tmeîîut is, tsu$, tewwet deg udem is, tenna d: ""tam$aôt tiâiqeôt?"""
  51,30,"Nnan: ""akka id Inna Mass im. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw""."
  51,31,"Inna: ""anwa ay d awal nnwen, a yimceggâan""?"
  51,32,"Nnan: ""nekwni neppuceggaâ d ar ugdud ibe$wviyen."
  51,33,"Iwakken a ten neôoem s uéôu n talaxt"
  51,34,"i ipwaôecmen s$uô Mass ik i ucmiten""."
  51,35,"Nessuffe$ kra illan, degs, n lmumnin."
  51,36,"Nufa kan degs, yiwen uxxam n imvuâen."
  51,37,"Neooa p id d assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  51,38,"I di Musa, mi t id Nuzen i Ferâun, s udabu n ûûeê."
  51,39,"Iaâûa, akked imalalen is, inna: ""d aseêêar, ne$ d aôehbani""."
  51,40,"Neddem it, neppa akked iâsekriwen is, Nveggeô iten ar yill. Tiyta degs."
  51,41,"I di Âad, mi sen Nuzen avu asexvi."
  51,42,"Ur ippaooa ayen immuger, alamma irra t am rrmim."
  51,43,"I Tamud, mi pwanecden: ""siwa tallit ara tezhum""."
  51,44,"Âuûan lameô n Mass nnsen. Tewwet iten id ssiâqa, nitni la pwalin."
  51,45,"Ur zmiren a d kren, ur pwasellken."
  51,46,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel, llan, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en."
  51,47,"Igenni, Nebna t s loehd, d Nekwni it Issewsaân."
  51,48,"Tamurt, Nessa p. Ay gerzen Wid Itessun!"
  51,49,"Di yal cci, Nexleq tayuga, ahat a d tesmektim."
  51,50,"Ihi, srifget ar Öebbi. Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen."
  51,51,"Ur sâut, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven! Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen."
  51,52,"Akka, ur iusi umazan ar wid i ten id izwaren, mebla ma nnan as: ""d aseêêar ne$ d aôehbani""."
  51,53,"Day ppuweûûan $ef waya? Xaîi, nitni d agdud izegren tilas."
  51,54,"Ïîixxeô asen; ur deg k tiyta."
  51,55,"Smektay ed. Asmekti, s tidep, infaâ lmumnin."
  51,56,"Xelqe$ leonun akked imdanen, iwakken kan ad iyI âabden."
  51,57,"Ur b$i$ segsen ôôeéq, ur b$i$ ad iyi cceççen."
  51,58,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Aôeééaq, d Bu tezmert n ûûeê."
  51,59,"Ih, i wid idensen, amur am umur imeddukwal nnsen. Ulay$eô iyI $eûben."
  51,60,"A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, ilmend n wass i sen ippuwaââden!"
